<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Rogues who let their Stealth drop below 1/4th of their level will get the specialization automaticly trained (8th, 12th, 16th, etc...), costing them no points, next time they visit their trainer. Only Stealth is automaticly trained for Rogues.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
